      <title>波多黎各董事会寻求听证会以修改公用事业公司的债务计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/puerto-rico-board-seeks-hearing-to-revise-utility-s-debt-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波多黎各金融监督委员会正寻求重启对该岛电力公司债务重组计划的确认听证会，此前上诉法院上周裁定，债券持有人有权获得该机构未来的净收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/puerto-rico-board-seeks-hearing-to-revise-utility-s-debt-plan</guid>
